ase"><span class=3D"strut"></span><span class=3D"mord">10</span><span class=
=3D"mord text"><span class=3D"mord">&nbsp;carats</span></span></span></span=
></span></span></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">Similarly, if you have a diamond weighing <s=
trong>15 carats</strong>, its weight in grams would be:</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span class=3D"katex-display"><span class=3D=
